s by “your public and private real estate investment solution” we mean that griffin institutional access™ real estate fund which offers investors a blend of public and private real estate investments selected and managed by leading institutions the fund’s subadvisors delivers an investment solution this fund because it provides an array of potential benefits from current income to less volatility and modest market correlation to pricing transparency and periodic liquidity is a ’solution’ close attention you are leaving the griffin capital company llc griffin capital webpage this external link provides additional information that griffin capital and its affiliates believe may be of interest to prospective investors griffin capital has no control over this external site and cannot attest to the accuracy of information provided by this link linking to an external site does not constitute an endorsement by griffin capital of the information presented on the site acknowledge and agree close understanding the risks  griffin capital about program details investment overview healthcare opportunity acquisition strategy risk factors management team corporate governance property portfolio forms  literature news  sec filings investment offerings investor  advisor  contact us griffin capital  american healthcare investors  investor login  access advisor tools about program details investment overview healthcare opportunity acquisition strategy risk factors management team corporate governance property portfolio acworth medical complex carolina commons medical office building chesterfield corporate plaza country club medical office building crown senior care portfolio dekalb professional center delta valley assisted living facility portfolio east texas medical office building portfolio glen burnie md medical office building independence medical office building portfolio king of prussia pa medical office building kingwood medical office building portfolio lee’s summit mo medical o