ith this option b alternative investment products available stay with first trust retirement and move your ira to another alternative investment complete the ira transferrollover form ftr ira application and the new sponsors subscription documentation sign all forms and mail to the appropriate address listed on the form ira application only required if ira account does not exist within product sponsor carter validus mission critical reits cīon investment corporation cnl cole capital cottonwood residential franklin square funds greenbacker renewable energy co griffinamerican healthcare reit iii inc griffinbenefit street partners bdc griffin capital essential asset reit inc griffin capital essential asset reit ii inc griffin institutional access real estate fund highland capital management industrial income trust inc  industrial property trust inc inland real estate income trust inland residential properties trust lightstone real estate investments mvp reits northstar healthcare income inc   northstar real estate income ii inc   provasi resource real estate rreef property trust inc sierra income corporation steadfast capital market group llc ira application kit steadfast capital market group forms   strategic storage ira application kit strategic storage   terra income fund  trilinc global impact fund triloma united development funding       the premier ira custodian choice of alternative investment product sponsors first trust retirement is the trade name of first trust company of onaga contact details phone  ftretire email ftrdstsystemscom contact information by product  copyright  by first trust retirement all rights reserved    legal disclaimer  press releases  griffin capital about property portfolio forms  literature news  sec filings sec filings  press releases  press releases  press releases  press releases investment offerings investor  advisor  contact us griffin capital  american healthcare investors  investor login  access advisor tools about program detai